        public static final java.lang.String BATCH_SF_UPLOADING
        Broadcast Action: S&F Upload begin
        "com.pax.us.pay.BATCH_SF_UPLOADING"

        Input: StatusData.PARAM_SF_TYPE sfType
        Type: String

        Input: StatusData.PARAM_SF_CURRENT_COUNT currentCount

        Input: StatusData.PARAM_SF_TOTAL_COUNT totalCount

        if sfType is SFType.STORED,
        display: "Uploading Store Transaction...\nTotal Count :"+totalCount+" Current Count :"+totalCount
        if sfType is SFType.FAILED,
        display: "Uploading Failed Transaction...\nTotal Count :"+totalCount+" Current Count :"+totalCount
